<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Alcatraz Documentation on Alcatraz</title><link>https://bolasblack.github.io/alcatraz/</link><description>Recent content in Alcatraz Documentation on Alcatraz</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://bolasblack.github.io/alcatraz/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Quickstart</title><link>https://bolasblack.github.io/alcatraz/quickstart/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://bolasblack.github.io/alcatraz/quickstart/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="quickstart-guide"&gt;Quickstart Guide&lt;a class="anchor" href="#quickstart-guide"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Get started with Alcatraz in under 5 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="installation"&gt;Installation&lt;a class="anchor" href="#installation"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="go-install"&gt;Go Install&lt;a class="anchor" href="#go-install"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#272822;background-color:#fafafa;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;go install github.com/bolasblack/alcatraz/cmd/alca@latest&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="nix"&gt;Nix&lt;a class="anchor" href="#nix"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#272822;background-color:#fafafa;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;nix profile install github:bolasblack/alcatraz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="build-from-source"&gt;Build from Source&lt;a class="anchor" href="#build-from-source"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#272822;background-color:#fafafa;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;git clone https://github.com/bolasblack/alcatraz.git
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; alcatraz
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;make build&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;The binary is created at &lt;code&gt;out/bin/alca&lt;/code&gt;. Add it to your PATH:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#272822;background-color:#fafafa;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;export&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;PATH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#d88200"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;$PWD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#d88200"&gt;/out/bin:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;$PATH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#d88200"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="basic-commands"&gt;Basic Commands&lt;a class="anchor" href="#basic-commands"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
 &lt;thead&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Command&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/thead&gt;
 &lt;tbody&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;alca init&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Create &lt;code&gt;.alca.toml&lt;/code&gt; configuration&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;alca up&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Start container&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;alca run &amp;lt;cmd&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Execute command in container&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;alca down&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Stop and remove container&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;alca status&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Show container status and config info&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h2 id="your-first-container"&gt;Your First Container&lt;a class="anchor" href="#your-first-container"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="step-1-initialize"&gt;Step 1: Initialize&lt;a class="anchor" href="#step-1-initialize"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Navigate to your project directory and initialize Alcatraz:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Configuration</title><link>https://bolasblack.github.io/alcatraz/config/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://bolasblack.github.io/alcatraz/config/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="configuration-reference"&gt;Configuration Reference&lt;a class="anchor" href="#configuration-reference"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This document describes the &lt;code&gt;.alca.toml&lt;/code&gt; configuration file format for Alcatraz.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="table-of-contents"&gt;Table of Contents&lt;a class="anchor" href="#table-of-contents"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#overview"&gt;Overview&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#includes"&gt;Includes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#field-reference"&gt;Field Reference&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#runtime-specific-notes"&gt;Runtime-Specific Notes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#network-configuration"&gt;Network Configuration&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#full-example"&gt;Full Example&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="overview"&gt;Overview&lt;a class="anchor" href="#overview"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alcatraz uses TOML format for configuration. The configuration file should be named &lt;code&gt;.alca.toml&lt;/code&gt; and placed in your project root.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="includes"&gt;Includes&lt;a class="anchor" href="#includes"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Configuration files can include other files for composable configuration:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#272822;background-color:#fafafa;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-toml" data-lang="toml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75af00"&gt;includes&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#d88200"&gt;&amp;#34;.alca.dev.toml&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#d88200"&gt;&amp;#34;.alca.local.toml&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="basic-usage"&gt;Basic Usage&lt;a class="anchor" href="#basic-usage"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#272822;background-color:#fafafa;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-toml" data-lang="toml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# .alca.toml - main config&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75af00"&gt;includes&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#d88200"&gt;&amp;#34;.alca.base.toml&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75af00"&gt;image&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#d88200"&gt;&amp;#34;myapp:latest&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Override base image&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#272822;background-color:#fafafa;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-toml" data-lang="toml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# .alca.base.toml - shared base config&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75af00"&gt;image&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#d88200"&gt;&amp;#34;nixos/nix&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75af00"&gt;workdir&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#d88200"&gt;&amp;#34;/workspace&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75af00"&gt;commands&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75af00"&gt;enter&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#111"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#d88200"&gt;&amp;#34;[ -f flake.nix ] &amp;amp;&amp;amp; exec nix develop&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="path-resolution"&gt;Path Resolution&lt;a class="anchor" href="#path-resolution"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paths are resolved &lt;strong&gt;relative to the including file&amp;rsquo;s directory&lt;/strong&gt; (not the current working directory)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Absolute paths are also supported&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id="glob-patterns"&gt;Glob Patterns&lt;a class="anchor" href="#glob-patterns"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use glob patterns to include multiple files:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Runtimes</title><link>https://bolasblack.github.io/alcatraz/runtimes/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://bolasblack.github.io/alcatraz/runtimes/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="runtimes"&gt;Runtimes&lt;a class="anchor" href="#runtimes"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alcatraz supports multiple container runtimes for isolating code execution. This document covers the supported runtimes, their characteristics, and how to configure them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="runtime-overview"&gt;Runtime Overview&lt;a class="anchor" href="#runtime-overview"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="auto-detection"&gt;Auto-Detection&lt;a class="anchor" href="#auto-detection"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By default (&lt;code&gt;runtime = &amp;quot;auto&amp;quot;&lt;/code&gt;), Alcatraz automatically selects the best available runtime:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
 &lt;thead&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Platform&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Priority Order&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/thead&gt;
 &lt;tbody&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Linux&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Podman &amp;gt; Docker&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Other&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Docker&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;blockquote class='book-hint '&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;macOS Users&lt;/strong&gt;: We recommend &lt;a href="https://orbstack.dev/"&gt;OrbStack&lt;/a&gt; as it provides automatic memory management (shrinking unused memory), which colima and lima do not support.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;h3 id="manual-selection"&gt;Manual Selection&lt;a class="anchor" href="#manual-selection"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Override auto-detection by setting &lt;code&gt;runtime&lt;/code&gt; in &lt;code&gt;.alca.toml&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>alca</title><link>https://bolasblack.github.io/alcatraz/commands/alca/</link><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://bolasblack.github.io/alcatraz/commands/alca/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="alca"&gt;alca&lt;a class="anchor" href="#alca"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alcatraz - Lightweight container isolation for AI coding assistants&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="synopsis"&gt;Synopsis&lt;a class="anchor" href="#synopsis"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alcatraz (alca) provides lightweight container isolation for AI coding assistants.
It wraps AI agent processes in configurable containers for enhanced security.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="options"&gt;Options&lt;a class="anchor" href="#options"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#272822;background-color:#fafafa;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; -h, --help help for alca&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="see-also"&gt;SEE ALSO&lt;a class="anchor" href="#see-also"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="./alca_cleanup.md"&gt;alca cleanup&lt;/a&gt;	 - Remove orphaned Alcatraz containers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="./alca_down.md"&gt;alca down&lt;/a&gt;	 - Stop the sandbox environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="./alca_experimental.md"&gt;alca experimental&lt;/a&gt;	 - Experimental commands (use with caution)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="./alca_init.md"&gt;alca init&lt;/a&gt;	 - Initialize Alcatraz configuration in current directory&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="./alca_list.md"&gt;alca list&lt;/a&gt;	 - List all Alcatraz containers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="./alca_network-helper.md"&gt;alca network-helper&lt;/a&gt;	 - Manage network helper for macOS LAN access&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="./alca_run.md"&gt;alca run&lt;/a&gt;	 - Run a command inside the sandbox&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="./alca_status.md"&gt;alca status&lt;/a&gt;	 - Show current Alcatraz status&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="./alca_up.md"&gt;alca up&lt;/a&gt;	 - Start the sandbox environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h6 id="auto-generated-by-spf13cobra-on-27-jan-2026"&gt;Auto generated by spf13/cobra on 27-Jan-2026&lt;a class="anchor" href="#auto-generated-by-spf13cobra-on-27-jan-2026"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h6&gt;</description></item><item><title>alca cleanup</title><link>https://bolasblack.github.io/alcatraz/commands/alca_cleanup/</link><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://bolasblack.github.io/alcatraz/commands/alca_cleanup/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="alca-cleanup"&gt;alca cleanup&lt;a class="anchor" href="#alca-cleanup"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Remove orphaned Alcatraz containers&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="synopsis"&gt;Synopsis&lt;a class="anchor" href="#synopsis"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Find and remove orphaned Alcatraz containers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An orphan container is one whose project directory no longer exists,
or whose state file (.alca/state.json) has been deleted.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#272822;background-color:#fafafa;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;alca cleanup [flags]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="options"&gt;Options&lt;a class="anchor" href="#options"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#272822;background-color:#fafafa;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; --all Delete all orphan containers without prompting
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; -h, --help help for cleanup&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="see-also"&gt;SEE ALSO&lt;a class="anchor" href="#see-also"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="./alca.md"&gt;alca&lt;/a&gt;	 - Alcatraz - Lightweight container isolation for AI coding assistants&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h6 id="auto-generated-by-spf13cobra-on-27-jan-2026"&gt;Auto generated by spf13/cobra on 27-Jan-2026&lt;a class="anchor" href="#auto-generated-by-spf13cobra-on-27-jan-2026"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h6&gt;</description></item><item><title>alca down</title><link>https://bolasblack.github.io/alcatraz/commands/alca_down/</link><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://bolasblack.github.io/alcatraz/commands/alca_down/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="alca-down"&gt;alca down&lt;a class="anchor" href="#alca-down"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stop the sandbox environment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="synopsis"&gt;Synopsis&lt;a class="anchor" href="#synopsis"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stop the running Alcatraz sandbox environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#272822;background-color:#fafafa;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;alca down [flags]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="options"&gt;Options&lt;a class="anchor" href="#options"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#272822;background-color:#fafafa;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; -h, --help help for down&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="see-also"&gt;SEE ALSO&lt;a class="anchor" href="#see-also"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="./alca.md"&gt;alca&lt;/a&gt;	 - Alcatraz - Lightweight container isolation for AI coding assistants&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h6 id="auto-generated-by-spf13cobra-on-27-jan-2026"&gt;Auto generated by spf13/cobra on 27-Jan-2026&lt;a class="anchor" href="#auto-generated-by-spf13cobra-on-27-jan-2026"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h6&gt;</description></item><item><title>alca experimental</title><link>https://bolasblack.github.io/alcatraz/commands/alca_experimental/</link><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://bolasblack.github.io/alcatraz/commands/alca_experimental/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="alca-experimental"&gt;alca experimental&lt;a class="anchor" href="#alca-experimental"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experimental commands (use with caution)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="synopsis"&gt;Synopsis&lt;a class="anchor" href="#synopsis"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
